Class GeneratorGrammar

java.lang.Object
  com.coasttocoastresearch.apg.Grammar
      com.coasttocoastresearch.apg.GeneratorGrammar

public class GeneratorGrammar
extends Grammar

This is a sample of the Grammar class generated by APG.

The Generator is a Java APG Parser, just like the Parser's it generates. The working version of GeneratorGrammar was generated from a bootstrap program built with APG version 6.1. This file, however, has been regenerated with the Generator itself. That is, the Generator can now re-generate GeneratorGrammar.java.

This file is an extension of the Grammar class which contains a number of members, member functions and enums not contained in the base class.
